cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper proposes a method for part-based representation for visual applications, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves detector learning, which is a machine learning task (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of spectral clustering, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method is evaluated on benchmark datasets, which is a common practice in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
